<p>Title: Best partners</p>

<p>Box 1:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>I met you at the dance party last year, when you was singing on the stage, attracting me like a light in the crowd. I didnâ€™t know you, so I wanna make friends with you.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Box 2:</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>We are best friends now and we perform together at the party tonight. You sing to the accompaniment of my guitar, and we make the perfect match in music. We are best partners on the stage. I want to know you more.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Box 3:</p>

<blockquote>
